summary: This is an out-of-office auto-reply email from a U.S. Attorney's Office employee, indicating they will be on annual leave from December 19-30, 2008, and referencing a supplemental declaration document related to the Epstein case.

events.title: Out of Office Notice
events.description: An employee from the U.S. Attorney's Office sends an auto-reply email stating they will be on annual leave from December 19-30, 2008.

keyFacts: The document is an out-of-office auto-reply email dated December 19, 2008.
The email references a supplemental declaration document related to the Epstein case.
The sender is from the U.S. Attorney's Office and will be on leave from December 19-30, 2008.
